/** @jsxImportSource theme-ui */ 
import { jsx } from 'theme-ui';
import {
  IonBackButton,
  IonButton,
  IonButtons,
  IonCol,
  IonContent,
  IonGrid,
  IonHeader,
  IonImg,
  IonInput,
  IonItem,
  IonLabel,
  IonPage,
  IonRow,
  IonTitle,
  IonToolbar,
} from "@ionic/react";
import React, { useState } from "react";
import { useHistory } from "react-router";
import TGWLogo from "../../components/TGWLogo.png";

const ForgotPassword: React.FC = () => {
  const path = useHistory();
  const [cellNum, setCellNum] = useState();

  const updateCellNum = (cellNum: any) => setCellNum(cellNum.target.value);
  console.log(cellNum);
  return (
    <IonPage>
      <IonHeader>
        <IonToolbar color="primary">
          <IonButtons slot="start">
            <IonBackButton defaultHref="/signIn" />
          </IonButtons>
          <IonTitle>Forgot Password</IonTitle>
        </IonToolbar>
      </IonHeader>
      <IonContent>
        <IonGrid>
          <IonRow>
            <IonCol>
              <IonToolbar>
                <IonTitle size="small">
                  Please enter the cell number associated with your account
                </IonTitle>
              </IonToolbar>
            </IonCol>
          </IonRow>
          <IonRow>
            <IonCol>
              <IonItem>
                <IonLabel position="floating">Cell Number</IonLabel>
                <IonInput type='text' onIonChange={(e) => updateCellNum(e)}/>
              </IonItem>
            </IonCol>
          </IonRow>
          <IonRow>
              <IonCol>
                  <IonButton type='submit' expand='block'>Submit</IonButton>
              </IonCol>
          </IonRow>
        </IonGrid>
      </IonContent>
    </IonPage>
  );
};

export default ForgotPassword;
